Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好捏\N{\fs38}Squeeze them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使劲揉\N{\fs38}Manhandle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大力不要停\N{\fs38}Give them the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好让它们爽一爽\N{\fs38}See if you can shuffle them. I mean, really get in there and knock them around.
