Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在对我做什么\N{\fs38}What are you doing to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty\N{\fs38}Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来五分钟\N{\fs38}Five more minutes of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要生气了\N{\fs38}And I'm gonna get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Je-jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我的错\N{\fs38}Not my fault this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呐\N{\fs38}Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frank 早上好\N{\fs38}Uh, morning, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"早上好" 你什么意思\N{\fs38}"Morning"? What was what is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在取笑我吗\N{\fs38}You making fun of me?
