Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frank  没必要动刀子吧\N{\fs38}Oh, geez, frank. I don't know if a knife is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用刀子也能搞定啊\N{\fs38}I mean, you know, y-you kind of had things handled without it.
