Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fs38}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去另外一个次元办点事儿\N{\fs38}I got an errand to run in a whole different dimension.
