Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick 你把Frank咋了 \N{\fs38}Oh, geez, Rick. W-what'd you do to frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显啊Morty 我把他冻住了\N{\fs38}It's pretty obvious, Morty. I froze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙\N{\fs38}Now listen. I need your help, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧离离离开这儿\N{\fs38}I mean, we got we got to get get the hell out of here
