Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是该给他解冻\N{\fs38}I mean, shouldn't you unfreeze him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿再说 \N{\fs38}I'll do it later, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事的\N{\fs38}He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs38}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 我要遇上Frank Palicky了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. I'm about to walk past frank Palicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是以后讲给我们孩子听的邂逅啊\N{\fs38}This is the story we'll be telling our children.
