Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术刀\N{\fs38}Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs38}Scalpel.
