Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经理给了一小时的午餐时间\N{\fs38}My manager gave me an hour for lunch, and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想"干嘛不来我老婆上班的地方看看呢"\N{\fs38}"Hey, why not swing by where your wife works?"
