Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 稳住了\N{\fs38}Okay, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 请务必告诉我你有非来不可的理由\N{\fs38}Jerry, please tell me you're here for an incredibly urgent reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐啊\N{\fs38}Well, it's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数千年来的三餐之一啊\N{\fs38}I mean, it's one of three meals that have existed for millennia.
