Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥\N{\fs38}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这个问题咱别再吵了\N{\fs38}Okay. Let's not rehash that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你很忙 我这就走\N{\fs38}I sense that you're busy and will now be on my way.
