Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这哔哔叫我听得见\N{\fs38}We can hear the beeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 来吧 Morty 我们走\N{\fs38}There she is. All right. Come on, Morty. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Oh, geez. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Oh, man, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个啥地方\N{\fs38}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是35c次元 这儿的气候非常适合一种特殊的树\N{\fs38}It's dimension 35c, and it's got the perfect climate conditions for a special type of
