Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树上有果子 果子里有种子\N{\fs38}And there's fruit in those trees, and there's seeds in those fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是奇异种\N{\fs38}I'm talking about mega seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种种子非常强大 我的研究需要这些种子\N{\fs38}They're they're incredibly powerful, and I need them to help me with my research, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我看了下四周\N{\fs38}Oh, man, Rick. I'm looking around this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点怕怕的呢\N{\fs38}And I'm starting to work up some anxiety about this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧\N{\fs38}All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 听我说 Morty\N{\fs38}Calm down. Listen to me, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道人在新环境里会感到不安\N{\fs38}I know that new situations can be intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看周围 又吓人又陌生\N{\fs38}You're looking around, and it's all scary and different, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎头而上 像一头公牛一样冲过去\N{\fs38}You know, m-meeting them head on, charging right into them like a bull
