Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要挂了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 深呼吸\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸点新鲜空气\N{\fs38}Breathe that, breathe that fresh air in, morty.
